title: Yamamori Noodles
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese restaurant with a number of veggie dishes, including tofu/shitake burgers, ramen soup with veg miso and grilled tofu, roasted vegetables with Japanese style curry, savory fried rice with tofu and cashews, and tofu and squash teriyaki. Also has gluten free marked on menu. A daily vegetarian bento box.
streetAddress: 71 S Great Georges St Unit D2
